  "room": {
    "id": 33415,
    "title": [
      "[Nereid's Cradle, Sharing Garden]"
    ],
    "description": [
      "Encircled by a picket fence, the public garden is arranged in steppes that are irrigated by fresh water pumped into the area by a complicated bamboo system that disappears up the incline to the higher steps.  Box planters are teeming with vegetation upon each of the grassy layers and are surrounded by seagrass baskets of harvested fruit, free for the taking.  A series of stone slab steps descends to the beach through a break in the fencing."
    ],
